parameters.name: AcceptLanguage
parameters.description:
The language of the response. Valid values:

*   zh: Chinese
*   en: English

parameters.name: FileName
parameters.description: The name of the file that you want to import.

parameters.name: FileUrl
parameters.description:
The URL of the source data.

> You must set this parameter to the URL that is generated by calling the GetZookeeperDataImportUrl operation.

parameters.name: RequestPars
parameters.description: The extended request parameters in the JSON format.
